snippet.title: JavaScript in Tamil
snippet.description:
Learn Javascript in Tamil. This is a full course on Javascript in Tamil language. 

This Javascript Tutorial for Beginners  Explains the following concepts:
The advantages of choosing Javascript
Difference Between Javascript and ECMAScript
How to use Javascript in HTML Page
Variables and Values in Javscript
Identifiers and Keywords
Number, String, Boolean, Null, Undefined and Object Data Types
Arithmatic, Relation, Logical, Conditional and Assignment Operators
Flow control with If, If Else  and Switch case statements
Repetition with While, Do While and For Loops
Built in Alert, Prompt and Confirm functions
Function Basics
Difference between Primitive and Reference Types
Objects - An Indepth guide
Different Types of Objects, Array, Date, RegEx, Math and First Class Functions
Detailed explanations of Array methods


Clicking "Like" button only takes a second. So please do so!
